  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA86">
<l>naviṉṟuraitta nāvalarka ṇāṇmalarkoṇ ṭāṅkē</l>
<l>payiṉṟataṉāṟ peṟṟapaya ṉeṉkoṟ – payiṉṟārta</l>
<l>meyttavattāṟ kāṇpariya mēkamaṇi vaṇṇaṉaiyā</l>
<l>ṉettavattāṟ kāṇpaṉko liṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The poets who utter [and] compose [poetry], taking day [fresh] blossoms,</l>
<l>what is the benefit they obtain by thus excercising? By which penance</l>
<l>shall I see today him of cloud sapphire colour difficult to see</l>
<l>[even] by true penance for those who are learned?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
